    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Robodies: Machine IS NOT Learning</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Teaching Has Never Been This Chaotic — or This Hilarious! (In VR)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of the <strong>grumpiest teacher alive</strong>, tasked with educating a classroom full of <strong>AI robots that… somehow forgot how to behave</strong>. They raise their hands, get distracted, fight, freeze, panic — and <i>you</i> are the last thing standing between order and total mechanical mayhem.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your mission? <strong>Teach them manners</strong> using… let’s say… <i>very unconventional</i> methods (absolutely not approved in real schools).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the most insane VR classroom ever created.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Control the Classroom… or Watch It Explode Into Chaos</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fulfill robot requests before their patience runs out</strong> — or brace yourself for total meltdown.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189480/extras/23cc769a2a1df3b8d036a106bc91a05f.poster.avif?t=1770227314\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189480/extras/23cc769a2a1df3b8d036a106bc91a05f.webm?t=1770227314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189480/extras/23cc769a2a1df3b8d036a106bc91a05f.mp4?t=1770227314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Write on the board, hand out books, and throw chalk</strong> to keep their attention (old-school tactics still kind of work).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Give misbehaving Robodies a good slap</strong> to reset their behavior — it’s wrong, but oh, it works so well.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189480/extras/f661f1a3f0ab83fade4a57e9e5a54f7b.poster.avif?t=1770227314\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189480/extras/f661f1a3f0ab83fade4a57e9e5a54f7b.webm?t=1770227314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189480/extras/f661f1a3f0ab83fade4a57e9e5a54f7b.mp4?t=1770227314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Break up fights, wake up sleepers, and repair broken robots</strong> before things spiral out of control.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grab, drag, or even toss disruptive robots</strong>, but be warned: unfair treatment might send them back <strong>possessed</strong>… and very eager for revenge.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every minute of survival is a miracle. Every completed lesson is a legendary victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189480/extras/21a0537022631f5e1538486aa8847d00.poster.avif?t=1770227314\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189480/extras/21a0537022631f5e1538486aa8847d00.webm?t=1770227314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189480/extras/21a0537022631f5e1538486aa8847d00.mp4?t=1770227314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Hilarious Satire of Out-of-Control AI</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the future, machines were supposed to be smart.<br>Reality check?<br>They’ve forgotten even the basics of proper behavior.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now <i>you</i> — a simple human armed with a chalkboard, a pile of chalk, and zero patience — must re-educate them in the fundamental values of society:<br><strong>respect, discipline, and common sense… one slap at a time.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s VR. It’s absurd. It’s therapy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189480/extras/5789ae662f685e45526262f0efb0d255.poster.avif?t=1770227314\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189480/extras/5789ae662f685e45526262f0efb0d255.webm?t=1770227314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189480/extras/5789ae662f685e45526262f0efb0d255.mp4?t=1770227314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Why You’ll Love Playing Robodies</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fast-paced, frantic gameplay</strong> that keeps you constantly on your toes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hilarious, unpredictable situations</strong> every single class.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique blend of <strong>chaos, classroom management, and slapstick physics</strong> only possible in VR.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High replayability: no two lessons are ever the same.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The perfect game to <strong>laugh, blow off steam,</strong> and create unforgettable moments to share with friends.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you’ve ever wondered what it’s like to teach a classroom full of misbehaving robot children —<br>or simply want to <strong>smack an AI with a piece of chalk</strong> —<br><strong>Robodies: Machine IS NOT Learning</strong> is your new favorite place to be.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189480/extras/10b93b193e036f507180c85f8a39af29.poster.avif?t=1770227314\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189480/extras/10b93b193e036f507180c85f8a39af29.webm?t=1770227314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189480/extras/10b93b193e036f507180c85f8a39af29.mp4?t=1770227314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
